OL,3,CAcid killer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cmurder conviction
OL,6,FA man who is serving life in prison
OL,7,Ffor murdering a man in an acid attack
OL,8,Fin Bradford has lost an appeal against
OL,9,Fhis conviction.
OL,11,FLee Calvert was part of a gang of
OL,12,Fmasked men who killed Barry Selby in
OL,13,Fhis bedroom in East Bowing in October
OL,14,F2013 by shooting him in the knee and
OL,15,Fthen pouring acid over him.
OL,17,FIn June 2014, along with three other
OL,18,Fmen, Calvert was convicted of murder
OL,19,Fand possessing a firearm with intent
OL,20,Fto endanger life. He was sentenced to
OL,21,Flife with a minimum of 36 years.
