OL,3,CAcid killer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cmurder conviction
OL,6,FCalvert appealed to the Criminal Case
OL,7,FReview Commission on the basis that
OL,8,Fone of the prosecution's key witnesses
OL,9,FRaymond Cowan had admitted that the
OL,10,Fevidence he gave was false as he had
OL,11,Fbeen asked to lie by the Selby family
OL,12,For the police.
OL,14,FThe Court of Appeal was told Cowan,
OL,15,Fwho is serving a prison sentence for
OL,16,Fburglary, was visited in jail by a
OL,17,Fprivate investigator in 2021 and that
OL,18,Fhe gave him a statement in which he
OL,19,Fadmitted lying to the police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
