OL,3,CAcid killer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cmurder conviction
OL,6,FA judgement handed down on Wednesday
OL,7,F26 March said the court did not think
OL,8,Fit was in the interests of justice to
OL,9,Fadmit the fresh evidence and that the
OL,10,Fsafety of the conviction was not
OL,11,Fundermined.
OL,13,FThe judgement said the court did not
OL,14,Ffind Cowan's integrity "so impeached
OL,15,Fby his evidence before us...to
OL,16,Fretrospectively impugn his evidence at
OL,17,Ftrial."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
