OL,3,CAcid killer loses appeal against
OL,4,Cmurder conviction
OL,6,FIn a statement in response to the
OL,7,Fjudgement, Calvert's lawyers Charter
OL,8,FSolicitors said they were "naturally
OL,9,Fvery disappointed".
OL,11,FThe firm said: "The question we asked
OL,12,Fof the Court was: How can an honest
OL,13,Fwitness misunderstand someone telling
OL,14,Fthem face to face in very simple terms
OL,15,Fthat he lied when he gave evidence in
OL,16,Fthe first trial?
OL,18,F"If Mr Cowan has made similar
OL,19,Fadmissions to others, then we would be
OL,20,Fgrateful if they would contact Charter
OL,21,FSolicitors."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
